  <refnamediv>
    <refname>ld_greaterEpsForNSteps</refname>

    <refpurpose> return true, when input is greater a constant for more than N sampling steps</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>

    <synopsis>[sim, reached] = ld_greaterEpsForNSteps(sim, ev, in, thr, N)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para><para></para>
<para></para>
<para> in * - input signal</para>
<para> thr - threshold constant</para>
<para> N - integer</para>
<para></para>
<para> If in is greater than thr for more than N time steps, reached = 1;</para>
<para> Otherwise reached is set to 0.</para>
</para>

    
  </refsection>


